      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cumberland_County%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "Bridgeton, the county seat, sees winter lows around 25°F and summer highs near 87°F, with a record low of –13°F in 1985.",
